history.content:
Many students are struggling to keep their productivity levels high with online schooling.

SKY at Berkeley, an RSO on campus, is organizing a Boost Your Productivity Workshop this Tuesday 10/5 at 5:30 PM PST.

This one hour instruction on the link between breath-work and productivity will equip students with an effective tool to keep their productivity high and the science behind why it works.

RSVP (to get the zoom link) at: tiny.cc/skyberkeley
history.subject: Boost Your Productivity!
